trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner gir støtte for utforming for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: It extends its parent class, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>, by adding a control-specific <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Det går sin overordnede klasse <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>, ved å legge til en kontroll-spesifikke <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>til den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>

trans-unit.source: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner does not render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner gjengis ikke den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the parent method to prevent rendering of the control.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer overordnet metode for å forhindre gjengivelse av kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: If there is no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A> associated with the control, the designer displays the standard gray box with the class name and instance name of the control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A>tilknyttet kontrollen designer dialogboksen standard grå med Klassenavn og forekomstnavnet for kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, no design-time rendering occurs at all because the check boxes and Web Parts titles are rendered by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome> instead of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> itself.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ingen utformingen gjengivelse skyldes i det hele tatt av i avmerkingsboksene og webdeler titlene gjengis av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome>i stedet for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>seg selv.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome>

trans-unit.source: Either an empty string ("") or the value of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml*>.
trans-unit.target: En tom streng ("") eller verdien for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup to represent an empty control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup til å representere en tom kontroll på utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: This operation renders the control as a gray box showing the class name and the instance name.
trans-unit.target: Denne operasjonen gjengir kontrollen som en grå boks med klassenavnet- og forekomstnavnet.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart"></xref> control and sets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewFlags"></xref> view flag to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Binding designer til det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart"> </xref> kontroll og angir de <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewFlags"> </xref> vise flagg til <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart"></xref> control associated with the designer.
Gets a collection of template groups, each containing one or more template definitions.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av malen grupper, hver med ett eller flere malen definisjoner.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property overrides its base implementation to add a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> object that is specific to this class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups overstyrer base implementeringen for å legge til et <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>objekt som er spesifikk for denne klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>

trans-unit.source: The appended <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> associated with this class.
trans-unit.target: Den nye <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> knyttet til denne klassen.
